name: Duck Dynasty - What the Duck?!?!?!
description:
Nope, not that Duck Dynasty.

This is a role playing adventure game to determine what kind of duck you are. Will you be an adventurous duck or become somebody's next meal? Will you become Hollywood famous or the next sports action star? Are you in search of love or in search of fortune?

Different routes lead to multiple endings. Can you uncover them all?
